The forward pass 
==================
The earliest start date for any event is the earliest finish date for all activites terminating at the event
When more than one activities finish at the single event , we take the latest of the earliest finish of those activities

The Bakward pass
--------------------
-> The latest date for an event is the latest start date for all the activities that may commence from the event 
->When more than one activities start from a single event we take the earliest of the latest start date of those acitiviteis.